  <brief_title>Dose-ranging Study of Once-daily Regimen of BAY 59-7939 in the Prevention of VTE in Patients Undergoing Elective Total Hip Replacement</brief_title>
  <acronym>ODIXaHIP-OD</acronym>
  <official_title>Controlled, Double-Blind, Randomized, Dose-ranging Study of Once-daily Regimen of BAY59-7939 in the Prevention of VTE in Patients Undergoing Elective Total Hip Replacement- ODIXaHIP-OD</official_title>
